Author: Andy Eticket4
Title: [TOKEN SALE FINISHED] Eticket4 - Event ticketing platform (Project is live!)
Body: After a really successful pre ICO, our company began to actively prepare for the ICO, which starts less than two weeks later, on February 27th. Our marketing team together with the advisors and CEO of the company Daniil Kruchinin starts the road show. As of February, several meetings with large investors have already been planned, participation in round tables and visits to international conferences, where we will talk about the project from the stage.  From 16 to 18 February (thanks to our CryptoBazar partners), we will participate in the conference The Bitcoin, Ethereum & Blockchain Superconference in Dallas, Texas, where such cryptocommunity stars as John McAfee and James Altucher, and many others are expected (you can see the program here).  Our presentation is scheduled for February 18, during which our strategic adviser Jevgenijs Vainsteins will present Eticket4 to investors, cryptocommunity and media.  However, our presence is not limited to this. Our other cool adviser, Ilia Stechkin, plans to organize a live stream (video and text) from a conference on our social networks so that our subscribers are aware of the most important events at the conference. (Actually, he was tasked with getting acquainted with all the journalists, giving comments to all the media and to smooth-talk McAfee to tweet about Eticket4 - let's see if Ilia will cope with this:))

Author: Andy Eticket4
Title: [TOKEN SALE FINISHED] Eticket4 - Event ticketing platform (Project is live!)
Body: ETICKET4 AND KATY PERRY‚ÄôS CONCERT IN SINGAPORE  An exclusive information available to you as a part of our community: Eticket4 will be selling tickets to the Katy Perry‚Äôs concert at the Singapore Indoor Stadium on April 8th! This is clearly a firm step towards expanding to APAC, isn‚Äôt it exciting? There will be an official announcement on March 23rd.  ETICKET4 AND FIFA WORLD CUP  Eticket4 has recently launched a stand-alone platform for football fans (for you?) who would like to buy FIFA World Cup tickets and visit Russia this summer. As you well know, the blockchain will be integrated in the fourth quarter of 2018, however, we would like to reward ET4 tokens holders much earlier and give discounts depending on the amount of tokens held. The discount system will be proposed during the last week of the token sale.  THE TOKEN SALE DATES  In view of the approaching APAC expansion the Eticket4 token sale has been extended to April 6th, 2018. In order to buy tokens please go to https://invest.et4.io (if you are planning to purchase less than 10.000 ET4 tokens) or go to https://sale.et4.io and fill in the KYC form (if you‚Äôre planning to purchase more than 10.000 ET4 tokens).

Author: Andy Eticket4
Title: [TOKEN SALE FINISHED] Eticket4 - Event ticketing platform (Project is live!)
Body: Greetings BitcoinTalk community!     Eticket4 is a secondary market ticketing platform developed by Israeli enterpreneurs, it is operating since 2016 and registered in BVI. Eticket4 has been selling tickets for major events in Russia and recently started to sell tickets for Katy Perry's concert in Singapore (check it out). Advisory board consists of people related to Huawei, e-shelter, Canonical (Ubuntu) (follow this link to read more about the magnifiscent Eticket4 team members). Please check the token sale website: http://et4.io and the platform itself: https://eticket4.com.  The Eticket4 platform seeks to expand functionality, incentivise customers and introduce a decentralized approach to ticketing. ET4 tokens are generated by the smart contract during Token Generation Event (TGE). The maximum number of tokens is 30 million.  Eticket4 ticketing platform exists and its functionality is already available to ticket brokers and ticket buyers. With the introduction of the blockchain-based functionality all token holders will contribute their efforts to its further development and receive new possibilities that would likely extend their knowledge of ticketing market and help them to take extra advantage of it. Effectively, the success and further development of the ET4 platform to a wide extent depends on the event organisers, ticket brokers and ticket buyers and the ways they prefer to use it.   TOKEN HOLDER'S ROLES  Take advantage of all the platform‚Äôs features: the token holder acts a platform participant, e.g. the event organizer, the ticket broker or the ticket buyer.       BONUS PREMIUMS UP TO 40%  Private Offer (Jan. 30 - Jan. 31) 40% (50,000 ET4+)  Volume-based (Presale, Jan. 30 - Feb. 21) 10% (1,000 - 2,000 ET4), 15% (5,001 - 10,000 ET4), 20% (10,001 - 15,000 ET4), 25% (15,001 - 20,000 ET4), 30% (20,001 ET4+)  Time-based (Presale, Jan. 30 - Feb. 21) 15% (5 Days), 12% (6 - 10 Days), 10% (11- 20 Days), 8% (21 Days+)  Volume-based (Sale, Mar. 5 - Apr. 6) 5% (1,000 - 5,000 ET4), 10% (5,001 - 10,000 ET4), 15% (10,001 - 15,000 ET4), 20% (15,001 - 20,000 ET4), 25% (20,001+ ET4)  Time-based (Sale, Mar. 5 - Apr. 6) 6% (5 Days), 4% (6 - 10 Days), 3% (11- 20 Days), 1% (21 Days +)    ANNOUNCEMENTS AND DISCUSSION While we would be happy to watch this thread and answer your questions, it would be great if you could join the telegram group as well. Telegram: @Eticket4_ICO Twitter: Eticket4_ICO.  TOKEN DETAILS Token Standard: ERC-20 Max Supply: 30,000,000 ET4 Soft Cap: 100 ETH Presale Hard Cap: 800 ETH Token Generation Event Hard Cap: 13000 ETH Initial price: 0.001 ETH  IMPORTANT LINKS WHITEPAPER (PDF, 10MB) TWO-PAGER (PDF, 7MB) TOKEN SALE WEBSITE - ET4.IO ETICKET4 PLATFORM Github / Code HOWEY Test  PUBLICATIONS Newsbtc.com (EN) Newsbtc.com Interview (EN) Newsvire.com (EN) Themerkle.com (EN) CCN (EN) CCN #2 (EN) Coinspot (RU) Telegra.ph (RU) Forbes Article #1 (RU) Forbes Article #2 (RU)  REVIEWS Digrate Review (EN) Digrate Review (RU)
